WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.714
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:01.714 --> 00:00:03.379
How are you all doing today?

00:00:03.379 --> 00:00:06.590
I have some things on my heart to talk to you all about.

00:00:06.875 --> 00:00:14.933
First off, I just want to say thank you for all the people who are liking and subscribing; you are such a blessing to us.

00:00:14.933 --> 00:00:24.132
I mean, I think my channel went in the last two weeks from 125,000 to 130-something thousand now, and I give all the glory to God.

00:00:24.132 --> 00:00:26.991
You know, people want to say, 'Brandon, are you a prophet?

00:00:26.991 --> 00:00:28.747
Are you a watcher?

00:00:28.747 --> 00:00:29.800
Who are you?

00:00:29.800 --> 00:00:33.560
' And I just want to tell everybody now, I'm just a person who prays.

00:00:34.093 --> 00:00:43.399
I don't label myself as anything; I just want to let everybody know I just love Jesus, and that's all that matters.

00:00:43.399 --> 00:00:51.236
If anybody wants to label me anything—like with the interview of Chris yesterday—people say, 'You're a prophet,' or 'You're this, you're that.

00:00:51.236 --> 00:00:54.040
' No, I'm a person just like you all.

00:00:54.040 --> 00:00:59.573
I come on here and I tell everybody that Jesus is coming, and that's all that I want to be called.

00:00:59.573 --> 00:01:00.855
I don't need a platform.

00:01:00.855 --> 00:01:03.790
I don't need my name in lights.

00:01:03.790 --> 00:01:09.160
I just want Jesus to be excited about me when I cross over, and that's all that matters to me.

00:01:09.160 --> 00:01:13.813
I want to tell you all this; this is very important that you understand.

00:01:14.267 --> 00:01:16.095
The Lord gave me this revelation.

00:01:16.645 --> 00:01:20.593
I wasn't going to go down this path, but it just came up.

00:01:21.267 --> 00:01:31.949
People are so focused on being something big in this life, and you're missing it.

00:01:31.949 --> 00:01:46.154
If you want popularity, and if you're wanting the world system to acknowledge you—fame, money, success—all that, you're in trouble.

00:01:46.154 --> 00:01:52.784
People need to understand that this life is a vapor, and we all see that.

00:01:53.168 --> 00:01:58.980
I feel like the older I get, the time seems to be going faster and faster.

00:01:59.600 --> 00:02:04.820
But one night I was praying, and the Lord showed me into the thousand-year ruling and reigning.

00:02:05.070 --> 00:02:08.529
He said the last will be first, and the first will be last.

00:02:08.844 --> 00:02:24.661
A lot of people that feel they're going to have great rewards in heaven are going to be shocked because of the fact that you did it all for praise on the earth.

00:02:24.661 --> 00:02:31.190
The Bible says that he that sows in secret will be rewarded openly.

00:02:33.140 --> 00:02:51.680
Even Jesus said praying in secret, giving in secret, doing things without having to have praise on this earth—basically, that is what I'm trying to talk about: volunteering at the church or cleaning a bathroom just because you love the Lord.

00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:55.328
You didn't have to have people say, 'Look at me, look at me!

00:02:55.328 --> 00:02:58.720
I just gave $10,000 to the church!

00:02:58.720 --> 00:03:04.742
' versus the widow who gave two pennies, but she gave all she had.

00:03:04.742 --> 00:03:14.600
Look at what happened to the people in the story in the Bible; Jesus was saying she was greater, right?

00:03:14.600 --> 00:03:23.251
So here we are again: Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:03:23.863 --> 00:03:32.269
When you do things in private unto the Lord, there's more reward to that.

00:03:32.269 --> 00:03:40.319
Now, if you're doing it, like I said, some people want to say, 'Hey, well, I just want to let you know I gave that person this or that,' you got your reward right there.

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:42.030
You're not getting anything on the other side.

00:03:42.030 --> 00:03:52.440
I'm just telling you, when we step over into that thousand years, you are going to be shocked when you see who's first and who's last.

00:03:52.950 --> 00:03:58.149
People have no idea the arrogance that they display in their hearts.

00:03:58.149 --> 00:04:10.616
The Lord looks at the core, the deep hidden things, the motives of why you do things, your thoughts, your intentions; everything, He looks at it.

00:04:10.616 --> 00:04:14.215
And I'm telling you all, He does it to me all the time.

00:04:14.343 --> 00:04:17.040
He says, 'Brandon, I'm monitoring your heart.

00:04:17.040 --> 00:04:18.060
I'm watching you.

00:04:18.060 --> 00:04:23.560
' And even whenever I have bad thoughts or I'm angry, He says, 'Check those thoughts.

00:04:23.560 --> 00:04:26.160
Change your thoughts right now.

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:28.973
' And I say, 'Oh, yes, Lord.

00:04:28.973 --> 00:04:41.053
' The closer you get with Him and the closer you walk with Him, He will correct those things, and it's all to go from glory to glory.

00:04:41.738 --> 00:04:57.715
So, I'm going back to this: when you get to the other side and you did all these things unto the Lord versus doing it for the praise of man or because of a wrong motive, I'm telling you, the Lord showed me.

00:04:57.715 --> 00:05:03.040
He said everything is based on seedtime and harvest.

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:03.640
Everything.

00:05:03.640 --> 00:05:08.620
Whatever a man sows, that will he also reap.

00:05:09.150 --> 00:05:13.000
And every seed produces after its own kind.

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:22.104
So, whenever He showed me into the thousand years, He said, 'Brandon, what you're sowing every single day of your life...

00:05:22.104 --> 00:05:28.274
' Every day you get up, we all have seven days a week, we all have 24 hours in a day.

00:05:28.274 --> 00:05:36.275
What you sow in that time, day by day, turns into years.

00:05:44.080 --> 00:05:49.759
That timeframe is the seed that you sowed for the thousand years.

00:05:49.759 --> 00:05:57.467
Everything you seed in that timeframe is what you will reap—good intentions or whatever.

00:05:59.091 --> 00:06:02.720
Your heart sowing that into the thousand years, you're going to reap it.

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:21.266
And the position you will have in that thousand-year ruling and reigning with Him, what you will do in those thousand years—I'm telling you all, I've seen it—it will be what you sowed in your life on this earth.

00:06:37.320 --> 00:06:37.700
How you walked in love...

00:06:38.760 --> 00:06:40.800
You have to walk in love.

00:06:47.941 --> 00:06:48.173
People say, 'Oh, you're being criticized all over the internet; are you going to respond to that?

00:06:48.173 --> 00:06:49.710
' And I say no.

00:06:49.710 --> 00:06:51.843
Love takes no account of a suffered wrong.

00:06:51.843 --> 00:06:57.220
No matter how bad somebody runs you down, you don't go back and attack.

00:06:57.220 --> 00:07:04.055
They have their opinion, they're entitled to it, but I don't have to allow people...

00:07:04.055 --> 00:07:06.340
They say, 'Why do you erase the comments?

00:07:06.340 --> 00:07:08.769
Why do you do all this stuff?

00:07:08.769 --> 00:07:13.659
' Because just as much as this is my house, I have to protect my people that come in here.

00:07:14.339 --> 00:07:18.390
You're not going to come and throw up all over my platform.

00:07:18.390 --> 00:07:35.813
It's my job to keep it, just like a pastor takes care of his church; he doesn't allow people to come in and just vomit all over the aisles and the stage.

00:07:35.813 --> 00:07:41.625
So, I'm not going to allow people to come and vomit in here.

00:07:41.625 --> 00:07:44.579
If you're rude, I erase it.

00:07:44.579 --> 00:07:48.639
My son does; I don't have time to read all that trash.

00:07:48.639 --> 00:07:52.000
But I'm going to tell you this: my job is to maintain love.

00:07:56.686 --> 00:07:57.159
Love takes no account of a suffered wrong.

00:07:57.159 --> 00:08:10.769
Regardless of how somebody is talking bad about you and running you down on another channel, the Bible says pray for those that come against you.

00:08:10.769 --> 00:08:12.452
Pray for them.

00:08:17.493 --> 00:08:17.911
Love on them, and that's what Jesus would do.

00:08:19.164 --> 00:08:26.816
He didn't go over there and say, 'Well, you Pharisees, I'm going to beat you up.

00:08:26.816 --> 00:08:29.328
' Jesus said, 'I love you, period.

00:08:29.328 --> 00:08:30.635
I pray for you.

00:08:30.635 --> 00:08:36.900
' And so that's where I have to stay: maintain an atmosphere of love because that's the greater glory.

00:08:36.900 --> 00:08:42.519
If you want to walk in the greater glory, if you want to walk in the presence of the Lord, God is love.

00:08:42.519 --> 00:08:45.739
It's not just what He does; it's who He is.

00:08:45.739 --> 00:08:47.119
God is love.

00:08:54.236 --> 00:08:54.552
And I want to abide in the Lord.

00:08:54.552 --> 00:09:03.208
'If you abide in Me and My words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.

00:09:03.208 --> 00:09:10.120
' But God is love, and that has to abide in you, and you remain in Him.

00:09:10.120 --> 00:09:18.899
I'm telling you, the moment you start getting off of that love walk and not walking in love, you're letting the devil rule and reign over you.

00:09:18.899 --> 00:09:26.835
All I can do is keep looking at you and saying, 'Lord, help me,' because I want Jesus to flow through my life.

00:09:31.600 --> 00:09:32.040
I want Him to shine on me.

00:09:32.040 --> 00:09:38.200
Whenever I stand in this seat, I take it seriously.

00:09:41.747 --> 00:09:53.012
I pray, and I feel the Lord has told me to come on here and tell you all what He tells me to tell you.

00:09:53.012 --> 00:09:59.439
Now, if you think I'm off, like some people do, then just click out.

00:09:59.439 --> 00:10:01.320
Click it off.

00:10:01.320 --> 00:10:07.448
You don't have to be hateful and rude.

00:10:07.448 --> 00:10:10.810
Just click off and say, 'You know what?

00:10:10.810 --> 00:10:11.580
Whatever.

00:10:11.580 --> 00:10:24.947
' My job is to just try to tell you what I feel like the Lord told me to tell you.

00:10:34.700 --> 00:10:34.880
So here's what I had for you today.

00:10:34.880 --> 00:10:43.396
That was a little side note, but I have something more for you, and this is important that you hear.

00:10:46.905 --> 00:10:52.296
I am not giving glory or any kind of praise to the devil at all; he came uninvited.

00:11:05.180 --> 00:11:05.610
But I want to tell you this because I feel like it's important because people need to know some things like this.

00:11:05.610 --> 00:11:27.628
One night I was asleep, and I was woken up in the middle of the night, about 3:00 in the morning, with Satan standing right in front of my bed.

00:11:27.628 --> 00:11:54.839
At this time, I'm going to go into detail—and I never do this because he's not worthy of it, he is a piece of trash—but people need to understand more in detail about things.

00:11:57.655 --> 00:12:05.307
I think a lot of times the body of Christ is real ignorant of a lot of things of the spirit.

00:12:14.106 --> 00:12:24.344
I try to just brush over things sometimes, but I felt in my spirit today to go into more detail about things, and then I'm going to go somewhere else with it.

00:12:24.344 --> 00:12:27.079
So, I just want you to listen.

00:12:27.079 --> 00:12:33.320
I was woken up out of my sleep, and the devil was standing right there.

00:12:33.320 --> 00:12:38.585
I'm going to describe him to you: he is beautiful.

00:12:44.102 --> 00:12:44.360
His hair is flowing down to his shoulders, but it is very beautiful.

00:12:44.360 --> 00:12:52.822
The layers of him...

00:13:15.160 --> 00:13:16.880
The way his face was, it draws you in.

00:13:16.880 --> 00:13:24.016
His eyes were as black as onyx—the blackest, most evil eyes I've ever seen.

00:13:24.016 --> 00:13:26.545
It was just pure evil.

00:13:26.545 --> 00:13:28.451
But his face and his voice...

00:13:28.451 --> 00:13:30.149
His voice sounded like music.

00:13:30.149 --> 00:13:32.760
This is very interesting.

00:13:50.275 --> 00:13:50.470
The pitch of his voice was perfect.

00:13:57.071 --> 00:13:57.347
The way his voice carried when he spoke to me, it sounded like a symphony.

00:14:03.579 --> 00:14:03.879
It didn't sound like musical instruments playing; it carried perfect pitch.

00:14:10.766 --> 00:14:12.388
The way it hit my ears when I heard it, it was soothing.

00:14:12.388 --> 00:14:32.737
His clothes were flowing, and it almost looked like one of those commercials when you put the fan in front of the model's face and the hair is blowing and it's very dramatic—they flip their hair and the wind is blowing in it like a fan.

00:14:41.355 --> 00:14:41.580
It was like that because his hair was moving like it was alive.

00:14:41.580 --> 00:14:45.937
But he had a light around him.

00:14:49.226 --> 00:14:49.461
He comes as an angel of light—deceitful.

00:14:49.461 --> 00:14:52.416
He's trying to mimic everything that God is.

00:14:52.416 --> 00:15:00.124
He's so evil, but he comes as if he's good, but he is not.

00:15:02.844 --> 00:15:03.893
He is deceitful, and he's an accuser of the brethren.

00:15:03.893 --> 00:15:14.200
At this time, I was laying there, and I was frozen in my bed with the most fear I've ever felt in my whole entire life.

00:15:14.200 --> 00:15:19.880
I'm just being real with you all; I couldn't move.

00:15:26.290 --> 00:15:26.680
I was just locked.

00:15:29.644 --> 00:15:41.035
You know when you come up on a dog or something very dangerous, like a poisonous snake, your body and adrenaline are flowing so strong you just lock?

00:15:41.035 --> 00:15:43.310
That's the way I felt.

00:15:48.575 --> 00:15:48.940
I just froze and I started praying underneath my breath.

00:15:56.152 --> 00:15:56.480
I was saying, 'In the name of Jesus, get out of my house.

00:15:56.480 --> 00:16:03.427
In the name of Jesus, get out of my house.

00:16:03.427 --> 00:16:10.413
' But I was saying it out of so much fear.

00:16:10.667 --> 00:16:15.160
He started laughing at me, and he was cackling the whole time.

00:16:15.160 --> 00:16:21.935
He said, 'I've come with a message for you.

00:16:21.935 --> 00:16:25.189
I'm going to offer you something.

00:16:25.189 --> 00:16:30.666
' At this time I'm just frozen, not knowing what to do.

00:16:30.666 --> 00:16:47.453
This is what I think is interesting: when you're seeing over in the spirit, he used the gift that I have, the prophetic, to be able to attain it.

00:16:47.453 --> 00:16:55.590
With seeing over in the spirit with the demonic, I was shown a vision.

00:16:55.590 --> 00:17:05.079
Now, he presented this to me, and in the spirit, I saw it as a vision.

00:17:09.101 --> 00:17:19.369
I see this vision of all this, and he says, 'I'm going to offer you anything and everything if you bow your knee to me and you worship me.

00:17:19.369 --> 00:17:30.777
' He said, 'I will give you your heart's desires of everything and anything you ever wanted.

00:17:30.777 --> 00:17:33.360
' And he showed me.

00:17:33.360 --> 00:17:41.200
I could see cars—Ferraris, Lamborghinis—massive houses on the ocean, all this stuff, piles of cash.

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:47.337
I could see piles of cash.

00:17:47.337 --> 00:17:54.823
He showed me all this wealth, a yacht—massive yachts—everything that your fleshly desires would ever imagine.

00:17:54.823 --> 00:17:59.440
He had it all spread out.

00:17:59.440 --> 00:18:09.760
'If you bow your knee and you use your giftings for me, I will make you wealthy beyond anything you could ever comprehend.

00:18:09.760 --> 00:18:15.662
' So, he takes me in, and I see this massive palace.

00:18:15.662 --> 00:18:22.120
It's the most evil, but he tried to make it look beautiful.

00:18:25.825 --> 00:18:26.170
It was black onyx—his throne.

00:18:26.170 --> 00:18:31.213
Not an altar; it was a throne—a throne that was pure black onyx with red rubies and diamonds on it.

00:18:31.213 --> 00:18:39.470
But remember I told you I went to the throne room with the Father?

00:18:40.520 --> 00:18:43.156
The Lord showed me His throne.

00:18:43.156 --> 00:18:48.493
He tried to mimic and mock the Lord's throne.

00:18:48.493 --> 00:19:06.840
But I told you living water was flowing from the Father's throne—the most beautiful, clear crystal water was flowing out of the throne of God, and it was coming into a massive pool on the bottom of the steps of the Father.

00:19:06.840 --> 00:19:10.493
There was beautiful water, and it was living water.

00:19:10.493 --> 00:19:17.187
Well, down the devil's throne was blood, and there was a pool of blood at the bottom of the steps.

00:19:17.187 --> 00:19:24.200
It looked like red-looking, nasty stuff flowing down the steps of this place.

00:19:27.255 --> 00:19:29.175
In the front, it opened up and then there were these two black-looking pillars.

00:19:29.175 --> 00:19:35.457
It looked like marble because it was like the Roman Coliseum, the way that was all designed.

00:19:35.457 --> 00:19:41.760
It's all chiseled out like those Greek columns inside his throne room.

00:19:41.760 --> 00:19:51.159
There were all these pillars going straight up; I could see the pillars in the spirit realm.

00:20:01.940 --> 00:20:02.320
The floor had the pool of blood, and it was all right before his throne.

00:20:02.320 --> 00:20:05.982
He had this decoration stuff; of course, he's satanic, he's the devil.

00:20:05.982 --> 00:20:11.000
But it was all around the floor; it was like this marble and everything.

00:20:11.000 --> 00:20:16.448
He was trying to show all his wealth of what was his in the earth.

00:20:16.448 --> 00:20:22.720
All I could do at this time whenever he was offering me this...

00:20:22.720 --> 00:20:30.650
I spoke out loud and said, 'I will never bow my knee to you, and I will never give my heart over to you.

00:20:30.650 --> 00:20:34.354
' There's nothing that you could offer me that I would ever want.

00:20:34.354 --> 00:20:36.870
I was so angry at this moment because I was frozen in fear.

00:20:39.780 --> 00:20:46.621
And there's a lot of you that don't believe in the baptism of the Holy Spirit and speaking in other tongues, but I do believe it, and I practice this daily.

00:20:51.456 --> 00:20:51.648
All of a sudden, I just started praying in the spirit.

00:20:58.311 --> 00:21:02.160
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, you have to pray in the spirit and you have to build yourself up right now.

00:21:02.160 --> 00:21:05.931
' And I started praying in tongues.

00:21:06.554 --> 00:21:15.931
And what seemed like literally the whole time I'm praying in tongues, he's laughing at me and he's mocking me.

00:21:24.840 --> 00:21:27.319
It was like a cackle—the Michael Jackson Thriller laugh—the whole time he's laughing, and I'm telling you, it was so loud it felt like it was echoing in my house.

00:21:27.319 --> 00:21:32.290
My son will play what it sounded like; it sounded like Michael Jackson's 'Thriller.

00:21:32.290 --> 00:21:36.343
' He's laughing at me, and I'm praying in the spirit.

00:21:42.600 --> 00:21:42.960
I said, 'In the name of Jesus, get out of my house!

00:21:42.960 --> 00:21:45.480
' And he's just laughing.

00:21:45.480 --> 00:21:51.093
But I'm in fear, and fear tolerated is faith contaminated.

00:21:52.213 --> 00:22:06.212
When you're operating in fear, you're not operating in faith because you have more faith in the ability of the devil to hurt you than you have faith in God to protect you.

00:22:06.212 --> 00:22:08.132
Fear is fear of death.

00:22:08.132 --> 00:22:13.131
So I'm in fear of him, and at that moment I'm freaking out.

00:22:13.131 --> 00:22:23.709
But I'm praying in the spirit, and I'm just praying, and it felt like it was forever.

00:22:23.709 --> 00:22:38.773
All of a sudden, I just felt that bubbling, that fire come up out of my belly, and I said, 'In the name of Jesus, you get out of my house now!

00:22:38.773 --> 00:22:52.640
' And all of a sudden, everything went, and he disappeared right in front of my face because fire came up out of my belly.

00:23:02.507 --> 00:23:02.720
Out of your belly shall flow rivers of living water.

00:23:04.760 --> 00:23:12.559
You have authority over the devil, but you have to understand who you are in Christ, and you can't be in fear.

00:23:18.491 --> 00:23:18.709
You have to build yourself up by praying in the spirit.

00:23:20.466 --> 00:23:25.808
You have to understand that Word and get that Word down inside of your heart.

00:23:30.107 --> 00:23:33.257
You have to understand that greater is He that is in you than he that is in the world.

00:23:35.200 --> 00:23:46.250
You can't be afraid because when the devil shows up like that, you've got to understand who you are and you don't entertain it.

00:23:51.760 --> 00:23:52.275
But this is where I thought was interesting.

00:23:52.790 --> 00:23:58.204
How do you know when the devil comes and gives you a vision?

00:23:58.204 --> 00:23:59.670
Because people say, 'How?

00:24:03.458 --> 00:24:03.662
The devil's giving him visions.

00:24:03.662 --> 00:24:12.535
' The devil is giving you these things; he's a messenger of the devil, he's not a prophet of God.

00:24:12.535 --> 00:24:14.305
I've seen that side.

00:24:22.140 --> 00:24:22.493
You know how you know the difference between the Lord and the devil?

00:24:25.746 --> 00:24:33.829
You can get snared very easily by a familiar spirit messing with the way the Lord has allowed me to, with my prophetic gifting and being a watchman.

00:24:38.364 --> 00:24:38.669
You have to be in the presence of the Lord through worship and His Word.

00:24:41.313 --> 00:24:48.187
You will have to know when you're operating in the pureness of the gift, which is when you're under the glory.

00:24:49.183 --> 00:24:59.515
When you are underneath the presence in worship and you are reading your Bible and you're praying, there is not a devil in hell that comes like that.

00:24:59.515 --> 00:25:10.543
When that glory comes in and that's whenever you start seeing over, you will get snared if you're just going around saying, 'I'm seeing stuff, I'm seeing stuff.

00:25:10.543 --> 00:25:16.129
' You're going to get snared by a demonic spirit, and it's very easy to do.

00:25:17.255 --> 00:25:17.662
You have got to maintain...

00:25:18.573 --> 00:25:33.783
when you're underneath worship and it's pure and it's coming out of you and you get under that river of praise and worship and you start seeking the Father and you're praying and you're speaking in tongues and He starts showing you things...

00:25:48.991 --> 00:25:49.209
that's how you know.

00:25:50.879 --> 00:26:04.060
You get over in the spirit by praying in tongues, and you get in there and worship, and you get in the Bible, and then you say, 'Father, show me scriptures to back up what I'm seeing.

00:26:04.060 --> 00:26:19.010
Give me a scripture to back up,' because I'm not going to get snared by some kind of devil coming in here trying to tell me something.

00:26:19.010 --> 00:26:31.180
You have to get in the river of praise and worship and you have to get in the Word and test the spirits.

00:26:31.180 --> 00:26:35.680
Test the spirits and see whether they are of God or not.

00:26:35.680 --> 00:26:37.399
If it doesn't line up, you're going to...

00:26:46.611 --> 00:26:47.103
and I tell you this: you'll have peace that passes understanding.

00:26:48.085 --> 00:26:56.022
The Bible says the sheep will know the Shepherd's voice and a stranger's voice he'll not follow.

00:27:04.080 --> 00:27:04.340
But when you're hearing the devil, there's torment because fear has torment.

00:27:17.449 --> 00:27:17.693
He is a devil that torments.

00:27:17.693 --> 00:27:21.074
That's why I say a lot of times, 'How do you know that's God?

00:27:21.074 --> 00:27:23.596
' Because they have peace.

00:27:26.074 --> 00:27:36.629
He said He will have perfect peace whose mind is stayed on Him because he's trusting in Him.

00:27:36.629 --> 00:27:42.919
How do you have peace if you're seeing destruction and a pestilence?

00:27:43.925 --> 00:27:46.500
You have peace because He is the Prince of Peace.

00:27:46.500 --> 00:27:51.200
When He flows with you and you abide in Him and His words remain in you...

00:27:51.200 --> 00:28:00.080
when you're close to the vine and you're close to Him and you're with the Father, you will have peace.

00:28:00.720 --> 00:28:06.800
You have joy, you have patience, you have kindness, you have goodness, you have self-control because He is love.

00:28:17.257 --> 00:28:19.332
That's how I do it.

00:28:19.332 --> 00:28:34.434
That's how you do it: you follow the voice of the Lord when you walk in love, when you pray in the spirit, and you read your Bible and you fellowship with Him with worship.

00:28:34.434 --> 00:28:40.445
He said He inhabits the praises of His people.

00:28:40.445 --> 00:28:43.520
That's how I keep myself clean.

00:28:43.520 --> 00:28:46.466
That's how I keep myself right before Him.

00:28:53.205 --> 00:28:53.460
And volunteering...

00:28:53.460 --> 00:28:57.900
don't take any praise from Him; don't take any glory.

00:28:57.900 --> 00:29:13.290
Always know that we have this treasure in earthen vessels so that the excellence of the power might be known of Him and not of me.

00:29:13.290 --> 00:29:24.720
I have this treasure of Jesus in this earthen vessel, but the excellence of His power will be known of Him.

00:29:24.720 --> 00:29:28.040
It's about Him and it's not about me.

00:29:29.261 --> 00:29:36.919
If you always keep your heart right before Him and you always give Him praise, He'll come and visit you.

00:29:38.910 --> 00:29:44.789
But if you start taking His glory, if you start taking what belongs to Him like the devil did, He's going to cast you out.

00:29:44.789 --> 00:29:49.440
Look at what the devil did: he tried to say he exalted himself above God.

00:29:49.440 --> 00:29:56.260
He wanted to become like God; he wanted to be most powerful, and he fell like lightning.

00:29:56.260 --> 00:30:00.350
Just always know that you never touch God's glory.

00:30:13.539 --> 00:30:16.864
Always keep yourself humble before Him, and in due time He will exalt you.

00:30:16.864 --> 00:30:26.177
Always keep yourself small in your own eyes, and you keep walking with Him, and He'll come and share His secrets with you because He knows He can trust you.

00:30:26.177 --> 00:30:28.000
People think they can fool Him.

00:30:28.000 --> 00:30:28.825
It's silly.

00:30:28.825 --> 00:30:35.909
God knows your future more than you know your past, and you can't pull a fast one over on Him.

00:30:35.909 --> 00:30:37.224
This is interesting.

00:30:42.689 --> 00:30:43.134
A lot of people say, 'The devil's talking to me.

00:30:43.134 --> 00:30:45.960
' The devil's a fallen angel.

00:30:48.212 --> 00:30:55.740
So if you can hear the devil's voice in the spirit realm, you can hear your angel's voice in the spirit realm.

00:31:03.720 --> 00:31:04.303
But an angel will never come and talk to you just to talk—like, 'Hey, let's go hang out.

00:31:04.303 --> 00:31:10.080
' An angel is there on an assignment to warn you about something if need be.

00:31:13.240 --> 00:31:24.270
The Holy Spirit tells you a lot of things inside of you, but if he comes to you—you entertain angels unaware—they'll come and say, 'Listen, don't go this way,' and he's trying to really protect you.

00:31:24.270 --> 00:31:30.480
They're sent to protect us, but they're not there to hang out with you and to be your friend.

00:31:30.480 --> 00:31:38.320
So don't be going around saying, 'I'm going to hang out with my angel today,' because you'll get snared by a familiar spirit.

00:31:51.080 --> 00:31:51.260
Angels are there on assignment to protect you.

00:32:00.494 --> 00:32:06.580
I commission my angels; I say, 'Angels of the Lord, I thank you, you are protecting us.

00:32:06.580 --> 00:32:14.973
' And I commission them from the north, the south, the east, the west to protect our home today.

00:32:15.262 --> 00:32:18.239
I call my angels—swords and shields drawn—to watch over us.

00:32:19.679 --> 00:32:21.440
I always give God the praise; I never praise an angel.

00:32:24.479 --> 00:32:24.760
You never worship an angel.

00:32:24.760 --> 00:32:29.1000
They are there to protect you, but they are not there to be worshipped.

00:32:33.298 --> 00:32:34.320
You can hang out with Jesus; you hang out with the Holy Spirit.

00:32:34.320 --> 00:32:39.453
He's the one that dwells on the inside of you.

00:32:39.453 --> 00:32:45.519
How do you know an angel's talking to you versus the devil?

00:32:52.210 --> 00:32:52.700
The devil's a fallen angel.

00:32:52.700 --> 00:32:58.320
Just don't talk to angels; talk to the Holy Spirit.

00:33:21.008 --> 00:33:21.386
I commission my angels all the time.

00:33:21.386 --> 00:33:31.060
'Go with my children and you protect them as they go to this place or that place.

00:33:31.060 --> 00:33:43.120
' I thank You, Lord, that You're sending angels here with us to protect us on the way to church or on the way to the grocery store.

00:33:45.875 --> 00:33:51.233
I send my angels with my children to protect them as they go to school.

00:34:02.064 --> 00:34:02.449
I thank You, Lord, that Psalm 91 says that they will bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:34:02.449 --> 00:34:06.439
They're ministering spirits sent for the heirs of salvation.

00:34:09.630 --> 00:34:14.399
I believe with all my heart that God's given His angels charge over us to protect us.

00:34:19.790 --> 00:34:20.200
I hope that blessed you all today.

00:34:23.660 --> 00:34:33.399
I need you all to understand that the devil comes to kill, steal, and destroy, and God said He came that we might have life and life more abundantly.

00:34:37.660 --> 00:34:38.190
I want to pray for you all today.

00:34:38.190 --> 00:34:42.919
Oh man, I almost said the Lord told me to tell you this also.

00:34:42.919 --> 00:34:47.973
He said, 'Brandon, you're coming to the last half of the year.

00:34:47.973 --> 00:34:50.090
Here we are; January's coming.

00:34:50.090 --> 00:34:53.333
What are you believing for in 2024?

00:34:53.333 --> 00:34:56.175
' The year's not over with.

00:34:56.175 --> 00:35:00.760
Do not give up on what you're believing for in 2024; this is not over.

00:35:00.760 --> 00:35:03.185
We've got half a year left.

00:35:03.185 --> 00:35:07.251
He said, 'Brandon, tell my people to believe for bigger.

00:35:07.251 --> 00:35:09.470
' Believe bigger in 2024.

00:35:09.470 --> 00:35:16.119
Believe that you can have exceedingly, abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:35:19.075 --> 00:35:25.933
I believe with all my heart that the better days of 2024—the wealth of the sinner—is laid up for the righteous still yet to come this year.

00:35:25.933 --> 00:35:28.510
There's still something supernatural happening.

00:35:28.510 --> 00:35:31.920
People say, 'Well, you believe a crash is coming?

00:35:31.920 --> 00:35:36.110
' Not before financial blessings for the body of Christ.

00:35:43.740 --> 00:35:45.491
I do not believe that we will see a massive crash happen before God's blessing for His kids to get us out of it.

00:35:59.920 --> 00:36:00.240
He is not going to allow us to go through all the drama if you are the remnant and you are seeking Him daily.

00:36:09.049 --> 00:36:12.480
I believe God is going to take care of His kids and that He's going to provide for us with the supernatural harvest before we see all the drama.

00:36:14.660 --> 00:36:19.111
He said, 'I've never seen the righteous forsaken or his seed begging bread.

00:36:19.111 --> 00:36:24.849
' And I believe with all my heart God's going to take care of His kids.

00:36:24.849 --> 00:36:34.000
If you're listening to Him on what to do and how to invest, I believe great days are ahead before a financial shaking happens.

00:36:42.839 --> 00:36:43.335
Father, I just thank You for every single person that is represented here today.

00:36:49.280 --> 00:36:53.800
I bless them in the name of Jesus, and I thank You, Father, for Your hand on this house.

00:36:56.665 --> 00:36:58.990
I thank You, Lord, for Your hand on their houses.

00:36:58.990 --> 00:37:06.424
I thank You, Lord, that You're protecting us and that You watch over us.

00:37:14.246 --> 00:37:14.680
Father, You said that no calamity would come nigh us.

00:37:14.680 --> 00:37:25.039
Father, I thank You, Lord, that we are Your children and we hear Your voice and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

00:37:25.039 --> 00:37:35.106
I thank You, Father, that You said that You would supply all our needs according to Your riches and glory by Christ Jesus.

00:37:35.106 --> 00:37:44.880
I plead the blood of Jesus over every single one of us, from the top of our heads to the soles of our feet.

00:37:51.235 --> 00:37:51.604
I call us well in Jesus' name.

00:37:51.604 --> 00:37:55.359
Call them healed and whole and well.

00:38:01.989 --> 00:38:03.171
I thank You according to Your Word, Father, that by Your stripes we are healed.

00:38:03.171 --> 00:38:14.205
I thank You, Lord, that we don't have to have sickness and disease in our bodies according to Galatians—that Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law.

00:38:14.205 --> 00:38:17.839
I thank You, Lord, that You've given us authority over the devil, Father; that You said we shall trample on serpents and scorpions and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.450
I thank You, Lord, that You said according to Your Bible, Father, that greater is He that is in us than he that is in the world.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
A thousand shall fall at your side and ten thousand at your right hand, but nothing shall come nigh us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.400
I thank You, Father, that we submit ourselves therefore unto God, we resist the devil, and he will flee from us in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
And Father, I thank You, Lord, for all those things that You promised us in Your scripture.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
I thank You, Lord, that we can be the head, not the tail; above and not beneath.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.750
Father, I pray for every single person that is watching this channel today, and I thank You, Lord, that they're refreshed and excited about life.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
They know that You said to believe for bigger.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
Believe for bigger, for exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
I thank You, Father, that all our desires of our heart...

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
You said You give us the desires of our heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
I thank You, Father.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
I thank You, Lord, that we are blessed in the city and in the field, coming in and going out.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.850
This is a good year—that 2024 is going to be a year that we soar and we go even higher with You, and that there is still half a year left.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
We give You praise for it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
All of August, September, October, November, and December—five months.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
You can do a lot in five months.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
So Lord, we give You praise and glory for it today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.500
We thank You, Lord, that You died on the cross and You rose again on the third day and You made it where we don't have to go to hell.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
Father, You paid the price for us, and Father, we love You and we worship You.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
We give You all the praise and glory for it in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Amen and amen.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Well, like I said, thank you all for joining me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
If you could, like and subscribe if you're not already subscribed.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Thank you for sticking around.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
Jesus loves you so much and we love you, and we will see you all next time.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
God bless you all and have a wonderful day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
